1592443827,"is_pvip":true,"replies":[{"id":"84333","content":"Markdown 并不能执行。","user_name":"作者回复","user_name_real":"郑晔","uid":"1258861","ctime":1592793176,"ip_address":"","comment_id":227620,"utype":1}],"discussion_count":1,"race_medal":1,"score":"10182378419","product_id":100052601,"comment_content":"我还没有到“设计一个 DSL”的高度，而且可能日常工作中遇到的问题也没有需要一门新的 DSL 来解决。<br><br>正则表达式、配置文件和 SQL 都可以算作 DSL，这些都是受众比较广泛的，如果是自己设计一个，使用的人没有那么多，还有意义么？<br><br>看了内部 DSL 的 Computer 的例子，感觉 DSL 不那么可怕了；顺便理解了为什么这“一连串的方法调用”可以被接受——因为这是一段声明 What。<br><br>反之，如果是一连串的动作，就应该避免了。<br><br>虽然短时间内估计不会有设计 DSL 的机会，不过“编写有表达性的代码”，“分离意图和实现”是我可以追求的目标。<br><br>看到留言里面有同学说可以把 Markdown 也当做一种 DSL，那么其针对的领域是什么呢，排版？","like_count":2,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":1258861,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/13/35/6d/07a42f81.jpg","nickname":"郑晔","note":"","ucode":"1EBD5AA5D4FC89","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":498718,"discussion_content":"Markdown 并不能执行。","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1592793176,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":true,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":""},"score":2,"extra":"{\"reply\":true,\"user_type\":2}","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":289761,"user_name":"林铭铭","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1068499,"ip_address":"","ucode":"AB392BEE7CD6A0","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/10/4d/d3/67bdcca9.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1619168506,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"5914135802","product_id":100052601,"comment_content":"内部DSL：groovy，scala，jruby，外部DSL：xml，json，yml。","like_count":1},{"had_liked":false,"id":254605,"user_name":"Janenesome","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1276572,"ip_address":"","ucode":"15D2673CC31D9D","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/13/7a/9c/a4bc748d.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1603157469,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":2,"race_medal":0,"score":"5898124765","product_id":100052601,"comment_content":"业务开发中，经常会被问到一个问题：为什么实现上面要加多一层接口，面向接口和面向实现有什么区别？我们用的是贫血模式，的确看不出太大的区别，好像还多此一举了。<br><br>面向接口应该也算是分离意图和实现，现在我还没能回答这个问题，希望看完专栏之后能写出更好的代码，并能回答同事们的这个问题。","like_count":1,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":1076652,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/10/6d/ac/6128225f.jpg","nickname":"jjn0703","note":"","ucode":"83AF403AC7DFB7","race_medal":1,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":true},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":394480,"discussion_content":"大佬，我也遇到这个问题，同事问了，我只能说是接口列出来，看起来直观，没有实现类那样一坨代码，看起来乱，不直观，不知道你学完这个专栏后，可有什么新点子，求分享~","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1631895221,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":false,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":""},"score":2,"extra":"","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]},{"author":{"id":1008468,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/63/54/c9475cd0.jpg","nickname":"cz","note":"","ucode":"96385190176F78","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":382046,"discussion_content":"感觉java里边遍地的一接口一实现有些过度设计了，如果业务上没有多实现的需求，但是代码里故意留个接口，然后只有一个实现， 严格来说就是 需求与设计的不匹配。\n\n通用框架开发预留接口是个很正常的设计，因为使用场景不同，有时候也会有替换实现的需求。 \n\n业务代码因为是直接对接具体的业务场景，需求是明确的。  实际开发中，业务需求的快速变更，可能导致接口根本无法稳定，差不多需求的变更就是接口的变更😅\n\n我更推荐定期重构，把一些稳定下来的代码分层，沉淀","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1625387484,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":false,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":""},"score":2,"extra":"","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":242377,"user_name":"旭东(Frank)","can_d